{"tid":672933,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A][SEGA 新創造球會 ROAD TO THE WORLD 每次1001都係唔開po(7)","createTime":"2018-05-21T11:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T02:32:29.000Z","uid":169231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d132ee62653e19b146fa008420f4e6aabb224d90","tid":672933,"uid":169231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"中文官網：<a href=\"http://sakatsuku-rtw.sega.com/zh/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsakatsuku-rtw.sega.com%2Fzh%2Findex.html&d=6g%2B1Ve69xbWfFfsVBHx%2BJAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d38c8d5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sakatsuku-rtw.sega.com/zh/index.html</a><br />\n日文官網：<a href=\"http://sakatsuku-rtw.sega.com/sp/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsakatsuku-rtw.sega.com%2Fsp%2Findex.html&d=6g%2B1Ve69xbWfFfsVBHx%2BJAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0dc31e1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sakatsuku-rtw.sega.com/sp/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n港版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sega.sakatsukurtw.world&amp;referrer=af_tranid%3Du0lLnCO4pd3Z3xeY4xIjBw%26pid%3Dsgc_officialsite%26c%3D20180419_preregistration\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.sega.sakatsukurtw.world%26referrer%3Daf_tranid%253Du0lLnCO4pd3Z3xeY4xIjBw%2526pid%253Dsgc_officialsite%2526c%253D20180419_preregistration&d=6g%2B1Ve69xbWfFfsVBHx%2BJAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=843db507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sega.sakatsukurtw.world&amp;referrer=af_tranid%3Du0lLnCO4pd3Z3xeY4xIjBw%26pid%3Dsgc_officialsite%26c%3D20180419_preregistration</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/HK/app/id1333024037?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2FHK%2Fapp%2Fid1333024037%3Fmt%3D8&d=6g%2B1Ve69xbWfFfsVBHx%2BJAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=163287c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/HK/app/id1333024037?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n日版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sega.sakatsukurtw&amp;referrer=af_tranid%3Df3rapR_PXzfXzphaBJrIpA%26pid%3Dsgc_officialsite%26c%3D20180419_officialsite\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.sega.sakatsukurtw%26referrer%3Daf_tranid%253Df3rapR_PXzfXzphaBJrIpA%2526pid%253Dsgc_officialsite%2526c%253D20180419_officialsite&d=6g%2B1Ve69xbWfFfsVBHx%2BJAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=df2b3254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sega.sakatsukurtw&amp;referrer=af_tranid%3Df3rapR_PXzfXzphaBJrIpA%26pid%3Dsgc_officialsite%26c%3D20180419_officialsite</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>新手留意：</ins></strong><br />\n首抽係完咗第一季嗰張綠卷 唔係事前嗰兩張(你亦可以當一開波送果800波係) <br />\n5星機率 2% 4星 25% <br />\n有三個陣容設定 set好唔駛次次入去重新set戰術 （但監督要）<br />\n平時留低3.5m 如果唔係出咗4星人 不過無錢買就喊都無謂<br />\n首抽樓主(尋夢人)個人建議 前鋒/攻中/ 防中 5星 如果有特定一隻想問可以回post問<br />\n相對上個人唔推薦： 卡斯米路(成日紅牌)   c朗 (技組比較雞肋同埋右翼唔一定每個陣都有)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>新手首要目標: </ins>盡量多抽既4星去砌陣滿足監督要求 (連鎖加成真係好高)<br />\n<ins>新手次要目標:</ins> 1.用最多同陣式一樣類型既人(有加成)<br />\n                                2.全隊盡量同一類型多既人 (聯技線可以上紅色)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>特別球員</ins></strong><br />\n4星抽既暫時比較特別係: 沙奧尼古斯 (DMF) 史密斯高文(RSB)<br />\n呢兩隻覺醒既資源比其他4星係少<br />\n另外個人覺得抽到盡量升：戴亞同甘賓尼( 因為覺2加技能發動 同技組係match到）<br />\n<br />\n世界杯: 如果見唔到朋友既球員你可以用自己隊既球員換人 就會見到 <br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>發掘:</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n買人                   監督<br />\n1星 1萬              1星 10萬<br />\n2星 8萬              2星 50萬<br />\n3星 60萬            3星 400萬<br />\n4星 350萬<br />\n5星 800萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發掘有8lv, 8lv 係你開曬所有聯賽就會有 越高lv  越大機率出高星人<br />\n4星lv7 之後比較多見<br />\n5星我打左36年先見過一次<br />\n聖誕樹同某兩個3星監督要8lv先會出<br />\n<br />\n抽人同買人分別<br />\n同星既話 抽既真人係勁過買既人大概500-800戰左右<br />\n所以會建議 抽既4星(AA技)&gt;買既4星(AB技)&gt;抽既3星(AB技)&gt;買既3星(BB技)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>新手問題:</ins></strong><br />\nQ: 幾時可以第一次十抽?<br />\nA: 五日正常應該夠有活動會早d<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 係邊刷覺醒材料？<br />\nA: D1 杯可以刷銅光頭, 其他光頭暫時好似未有得刷,只得某幾個杯賽首次獎勵 (有頭髮果個係叫覺醒練習LV.X 光頭係特別覺醒練習)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 幾時十抽好<br />\nA: 宜加都係唔錯既時候 因為有保底4星<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://gamy.jp/sakatsuku\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamy.jp%2Fsakatsuku&d=6g%2B1Ve69xbWfFfsVBHx%2BJAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a82dc7c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://gamy.jp/sakatsuku</a><br />\n<br />\n日本攻略網，有齊球員能力數值</span>"},{"pid":"e40addc88831a9f2cc837c6925f4f868434b573f","tid":672933,"uid":169231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/190807_6cd6d979f1a4b5b095f23d72b747df39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F190807_6cd6d979f1a4b5b095f23d72b747df39.jpg&h=87d06144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/190807_882e2fefcb35402d3186ea99e704d6db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F190807_882e2fefcb35402d3186ea99e704d6db.jpg&h=f3b10582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/190808_995284bb29a99e7c8ca4600f32fb88c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F190808_995284bb29a99e7c8ca4600f32fb88c9.jpg&h=17a35d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/190808_b1d28fa8a1ccaff1a040bafa03be60c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F190808_b1d28fa8a1ccaff1a040bafa03be60c5.jpg&h=017ffe09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/190808_50f90a3c917b75241c8af184b1f11e85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna